            "title": "PM2.5 polluters disproportionately and systemically affect people of color in the United States",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Christopher W.",
                    "lastName": "Tessum"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
